Capitec is well known for its affordable transaction fees. Their banking app is used by a rapidly growing audience of 1.8 million users. This is due to the convenience of the app. You can basically do everything on the app and never need to go to the bank. Skip the line, save the time. Capitec has also grown their credit card clients to a total of 360 000, due to very low interest rates. Here is some interesting information about Capitec  The bank fees for 2019 have significantly decreased compared to last year. Below is a comparison between bank fees of 2018, and bank fees of 2019.  In an economy which is becoming more expensive each passing day it is a breath of fresh air to see that some businesses still giving their customers a break.